%F A087445 a(n) = 6*(n-1) - (-1)^n. - _Rolf Pleisch_, Aug 04 2009
%F A087445 a(n) = 12*n - a(n-1) - 18 (with a(1)=1). - _Vincenzo Librandi_, Aug 08 2010
